          <En>A notice or announcement in a newspaper, magazine, or other medium, typically promoting a product or service.</En>
          <Example>The company placed a full-page advert in the Sunday newspaper to launch its new smartphone.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
